The '''League hall''' in a [[player-owned house]] is a room where the player can display various [[league]] achievements. This room can be created with 27 [[Construction]] and {{Coins|15000}}.

There are 7 [[hotspot]]s available:
* [[Banner stand space]]
* [[Rug space]]
* [[Outfit stand space]]
* [[Pedestal space]] x3
* [[Accomplishment scroll space]]
* [[Statue space]]
* [[Trophy case space]]

